---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---

<footer class="border-t border-border/70 bg-card/60">
  <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 py-10 md:grid-cols-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-2">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">cortel blog</p>
      <p class="max-w-md text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        Insight praktis seputar frontend, UI engineering, dan workflow product team untuk bantu kamu
        shipping lebih cepat dengan kualitas yang tetap konsisten.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-muted-foreground">Update konten reguler • Build stack: Astro + Sanity</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-foreground">Explore</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground">Home</a>
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-foreground">Artikel Terbaru</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-foreground">Topics</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
        <span>Frontend Architecture</span>
        <span>Design System</span>
        <span>Product Engineering</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-border/70 py-4 text-center text-[11px] text-muted-foreground">
    © {year} cortel blog. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</footer>
